{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"毛主席的信是春风","authors":["艾农"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":3,"day":5}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的信是春风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗大的红字暖人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席给咱来了信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的信是春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵吹得山河动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大抓革命狠促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱贫下中农齐心干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干部争先来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕战场大摆开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人欢马叫干劲高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车车积雪田里倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收图景在胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想挂了帅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争一颗粮食争一颗宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援革命不能少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握一把春泥乐心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定要革命、生产双丰收！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}